Seasons Greetings, Paul!

Take your holiday shopping list to Vail, Keystone, Breckenridge,
or Beaver Creek this weekend.  A day of skiing or riding, and a
day of shopping...what could be better?  From unique galleries
and resort shops, to factory outlet stores in Silverthorne, you
can be sure to find something for everyone on your list.  Don't
forget, Vail's Blue Sky Basin opens this Saturday!

