VAIL - http://www.vail.com

TONS OF SNOW IN VAIL!
Vail's total snowfall for the season of 95 inches puts the
resort more than 20% ahead of its annual historical average
of 73 inches for this time of the year.  There will be even
more terrain available this weekend with the opening of
China Bowl, Siberia Bowl, Golden Peak and Blue Sky Basin,
bringing the grand total to 5,289 skiable acres.  Adventure
Ridge, Vail's mountain-top activity center, also opens this
weekend offering activities such as tubing, laser tag, thrill
sledding, snow biking, kids snowmobiling, ice skating and
MORE!  For more information, call the Activities Desk
at 970-476-9090.

TIVOLI LODGE - Vail Village
From $89 per lodge room
Continental breakfast is included.
Rate valid 12/4-12/15/01
Call 1-800-451-4756 for reservations.

VAIL RACQUET CLUB - East Vail
$100 per one-bedroom condominium
$132 per two-bedroom condominium
Two-night minimum stay required.
Rates valid 12/11-12/19/01
Call 1-800-428-4840 for reservations.

*************************************************
BRECKENRIDGE - http://www.breckenridge.com

Peak 8 opens this Friday with 5 lifts, 580 additional acres
and the legendary Freeway Terrain Park, for a total of 12
lifts, 70 trails and 1047 acres!  With Peaks 8, 9 and 10 open,
there's no better time to work on your skills with a ski or
snowboard lesson.  Don't miss our Get Back To Skiing and
Riding America offer at to get 50% off all Ski & Ride
school class lessons before December 21, 2001 at
http://promotions.snow.com/1113200156.asp  Make your
plans now for The Vans Triple Crown of Snowboarding,
which has been re-scheduled for December 18-22. To learn
more about early season events and discounts visit our
website or call 1-800-789-7669.

BRECK MTN LODGE: $57 per hotel room
Call 1-888-893-9870 for reservations.
VILLAGE AT BRECKENRIDGE: $75 per hotel room
Call 1-888-459-7829 for reservations.
*Rates valid 12/11-12/17/01

